I shouldn't have you arrested.

741
01:30:08,821 --> 01:30:10,823
- It's that one.
- Yeah.

742
01:30:10,989 --> 01:30:12,533
- See?
- OK.

743
01:30:12,699 --> 01:30:14,159
Sam, where you goin'?

744
01:30:14,993 --> 01:30:18,497
Benny, this is exactly
what we were trying to avoid.

745
01:30:18,664 --> 01:30:22,251
By now, Joon would be in a caring
and controlled environment.

746
01:30:22,418 --> 01:30:25,838
Isn't it obvious now that
you two need some distance?

747
01:30:26,004 --> 01:30:28,340
Why don't we ask Joon what she wants?

748
01:30:31,301 --> 01:30:33,470
Sam, what are you doin'?

749
01:30:36,473 --> 01:30:39,435
Hey, Sam, come on!
Get down, right now!

750
01:30:40,185 --> 01:30:42,229
I don't know exactly what I want.

751
01:30:44,356 --> 01:30:49,695
I do know... that I am tired of
everyone telling me what to do.

752
01:30:52,698 --> 01:30:54,825
Sam, come on!

753
01:30:54,992 --> 01:30:56,869
Don't touch that!

754
01:30:57,035 --> 01:30:59,204
Sam, leave that!
I'm beggin' you!

755
01:30:59,872 --> 01:31:02,291
Joon, we want what's best for you.

756
01:31:03,542 --> 01:31:05,586
I know that.

757
01:31:14,845 --> 01:31:16,638
I...

758
01:31:17,306 --> 01:31:19,391
Sam, come down now!

759
01:31:21,560 --> 01:31:23,562
You're gonna get in trouble!

760
01:31:23,729 --> 01:31:25,814
I think I want to try
living in my own apartment.

761
01:31:41,580 --> 01:31:44,291
...I don't know.

762
01:31:45,501 --> 01:31:47,586
Sam, stop swinging!

763
01:31:51,840 --> 01:31:54,051
But I'm willing to let you try.

764
01:31:56,762 --> 01:31:59,348
I'll prepare the papers for her release.

765
01:32:00,766 --> 01:32:02,851
Thank you, Dr. Garvey.

766
01:32:05,938 --> 01:32:08,190
Come down!
Sam!

767
01:32:14,404 --> 01:32:16,490
Are you OK?

768
01:32:35,884 --> 01:32:37,970
I know.

769
01:32:38,887 --> 01:32:40,973
Me, too.

770
01:32:42,891 --> 01:32:44,977
I'm gonna check you out, OK?

771
01:32:50,691 --> 01:32:51,900
OK.

772
01:34:22,324 --> 01:34:25,285
Haven't we tried this before?

773
01:34:25,452 --> 01:34:28,497
Yeah, but my life's
a lot less complicated now.

774
01:34:31,792 --> 01:34:34,294
- Is Joon inside?
- Yeah.

775
01:34:34,461 --> 01:34:36,588
OK.

